OL,3,CBoys' reading remains in crisis as
OL,4,Cgender gap widens, report shows
OL,6,FBestselling author Anthony Horowitz
OL,7,Fhas warned there is a "war" between
OL,8,Fbooks and smartphones, as new figures
OL,9,Freveal the biggest gender gap in
OL,10,Fchildren's reading enjoyment ever
OL,11,Frecorded.
OL,13,FThe creator of the Alex Rider series
OL,14,Ftold ITV News that social media is
OL,15,F"the enemy of children" and warned
OL,16,Fyoung people risk missing out on the
OL,17,Fbenefits of reading for pleasure.
OL,26,@oD@WOUoD@[O]wD@AOUwD@WO]
