OL,3,CBoys' reading remains in crisis as
OL,4,Cgender gap widens, report shows
OL,6,FEleven-year-old Briella told ITV News
OL,7,Fthat when she goes onto YouTube on her
OL,8,Fphone, it's difficult to stop.
OL,10,F"I tend to do that a lot because when
OL,11,FI'm there, it's hard for me to get off
OL,12,Fit, but I try my best."
OL,14,FThe three boys we spoke with - Jack,
OL,15,FHarry and Roman - all enjoyed reading,
OL,16,Fbut did so less often than their
OL,17,Ffemale classmates.
OL,26,@rD@AOUtD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/14
