PN,30608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1781161488
OL,3,CBoys' reading remains in crisis as
OL,4,Cgender gap widens, report shows
OL,6,FHorowitz, whose Alex Rider series has
OL,7,Fsold more than 20 million copies
OL,8,Fworldwide, said the answer is not
OL,9,Fsimply telling children they should
OL,10,Fread.
OL,12,F"If you hold up a book and say 'this
OL,13,Fis good for you', that's a turn off,"
OL,14,Fhe said.
OL,16,F"If books are part of your daily
OL,17,Fconversation, if the whole family is
OL,18,Finvested in reading and literacy and
OL,19,Fbooks, then it will just by symbiosis
OL,20,Ffind its way into children and they
OL,21,Fwill read."
OL,26,@tD@AOUuD@eO]xD@AOU}D@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1781161488
OL,3,CBoys' reading remains in crisis as
OL,4,Cgender gap widens, report shows
OL,6,FDespite creating one of the most
OL,7,Fsuccessful series for engaging
OL,8,Freluctant young readers, particularly
OL,9,Fboys, Horowitz said he believes the
OL,10,Fdebate should not focus solely on
OL,11,Fgender.
OL,13,F"When it comes to this boy versus
OL,14,Fgirls debate, I'm not sure how helpful
OL,15,Fit is actually," he said.
OL,17,F"What we should be talking about much
OL,18,Fmore is the demographic backgrounds of
OL,19,Fchildren... children in less
OL,20,Fprivileged areas of this country who
OL,21,Fare the ones who generally don't read.
OL,26,@uD@AOUwD@PO]yD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
