OL,3,CBoys' reading remains in crisis as
OL,4,Cgender gap widens, report shows
OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,F"I think that's a conversation that is
OL,12,Fmore useful and that you can do
OL,13,Fsomething about because you can focus
OL,14,Fyour activities where they're needed."
OL,16,FThe National Literacy Trust says the
OL,17,Fgap in reading enjoyment between
OL,18,Fchildren from disadvantaged
OL,19,Fbackgrounds and their peers has also
OL,20,Fwidened.
OL,26,@sD@AOUvD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
